{% comment %}
  FAQ Section Component
  Reduces friction and increases conversions
{% endcomment %}

<div class="faq-section">
  <h2 class="faq-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  
  <div class="faq-list">
    
    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>What materials are the water bottles made from?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Our water bottles are made from premium BPA-free stainless steel with double-wall vacuum insulation. They keep drinks cold for 24 hours and hot for 12 hours. All materials are food-grade and completely safe.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>How long does personalization take?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Standard orders ship within 3-5 business days. Personalized bottles are carefully crafted and typically ship within 5-7 business days. Rush processing is available for an additional fee if you need it sooner!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Is the personalization permanent?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Yes! We use professional laser engraving technology that creates a permanent design. It won't fade, peel, or wear off over time. Your personalization is guaranteed to last as long as your bottle.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Can I wash my personalized bottle in the dishwasher?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We recommend hand washing with warm soapy water to maintain the bottle's insulation properties and finish. The personalization is dishwasher-safe, but hand washing will keep your bottle looking new longer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>What if I make a mistake in my personalization?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Please double-check your personalization before ordering! We print exactly what you enter. If you notice an error immediately after ordering, contact us within 2 hours and we'll do our best to help.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Do you offer bulk discounts for teams or events?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Absolutely! We offer tiered discounts: 10% off for 3+ bottles, 15% off for 5+ bottles, and 20% off for 10+ bottles. For orders over 25 bottles, contact us for custom corporate pricing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>What's your return policy?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>We want you to love your bottle! Non-personalized items can be returned within 30 days. Due to the custom nature of personalized bottles, they are final sale unless there's a manufacturing defect.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
        <span>Do you ship internationally?</span>
        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Currently, we ship within the continental United States. International shipping is coming soon! Sign up for our email list to be notified when we expand shipping options.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
.faq-section {
  margin: 40px 0;
  padding: 30px 0;
  border-top: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
}

.faq-title {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 600;
  margin: 0 0 25px;
  color: #333;
  text-align: center;
}

.faq-list {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.faq-item {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
}

.faq-item:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}

.faq-question {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  background: white;
  border: none;
  text-align: left;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #333;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}

.faq-question:hover {
  background: #f8f9fa;
}

.faq-question[aria-expanded="true"] {
  background: #f0f7ff;
  color: #0066cc;
}

.faq-icon {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1;
  transition: transform 0.3s;
  color: #0066cc;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-left: 15px;
}

.faq-question[aria-expanded="true"] .faq-icon {
  transform: rotate(45deg);
}

.faq-answer {
  max-height: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
  transition: max-height 0.3s ease-out, padding 0.3s ease-out;
  background: #fafafa;
}

.faq-item.active .faq-answer {
  max-height: 500px;
  padding: 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
}

.faq-answer p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #555;
}

@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .faq-title {
    font-size: 24px;
  }
  
  .faq-question {
    padding: 15px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  
  .faq-answer p {
    font-size: 14px;
  }
}
</style>
